<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="sv">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Köp &amp; Sälj Bostad Privat – Så enkelt är det</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <style>
    body{
      margin:0;
      font-family:"Segoe UI",Arial,sans-serif;
      background:#ffffff;
      color:#222;
      text-align:center;
    }
    header{padding:60px 20px 40px;}
    h1{font-size:2.5rem;margin:0 0 10px;}
    p.tagline{font-size:1.2rem;margin:0 0 40px;color:#555;}
    .steps{display:flex;justify-content:center;gap:30px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin:0 auto 40px;max-width:800px;}
    .step{width:160px;}
    .circle{width:80px;height:80px;border-radius:50%;background:#004aa9;color:#fff;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:2rem;margin:0 auto 10px;}
    h2{font-size:1rem;margin:0 0 6px;}
    .btn{display:inline-block;padding:14px 28px;background:#004aa9;color:#fff;text-decoration:none;border-radius:4px;font-size:1rem;margin-bottom:60px;}
    footer{font-size:.8rem;color:#777;padding:20px;}
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <h1>Sälj din bostad privat</h1>
    <p class="tagline">Tre enkla steg – inga mäklaravgifter, inga krångel</p>
  </header>

  <div class="steps">
    <div class="step">
      <div class="circle">1</div>
      <h2>Skapa annons</h2>
      <p>Lägg upp bilder &amp; prisförslag</p>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <div class="circle">2</div>
      <h2>Chatta &amp; visa</h2>
      <p>Boka visning direkt i appen</p>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <div class="circle">3</div>
      <h2>Signera digitalt</h2>
      <p>Kontrakt &amp; betalning säkras</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <a href="/detaljer" class="btn">Se hur det fungerar →</a>

  <footer>
    Läs <a href="/detaljer">detaljerna</a> innan du säljer eller köper.
  </footer>
</body>
</html>